 of Aby Warburg, with whom Benjamin unsuccessfully attempted an intellectual exchange.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aArt. 4aLiterary Studies -- General Criticism and Theory. 4aPhilosophy. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertStanford University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080478481840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804784818423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804784818/original  a978-3-11-070420-4  Stanford University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles